{"id": 2327, "genre": 1001, "title": "随着年龄增长，你身上都发生了哪些不可逆的微妙变化？", "description": "如果把变老当版本更新，你觉得自己都迭代了哪些功能？（题图来自：视觉中国 ©️ Ikon Images）", "record_count": 6140, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201805071103121vol3Nc0BnkufjyZ.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-07-05T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 291072, "content": "我真的只能依靠着自己\n接受可能没有任何人会爱我的事实", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1265183}, {"id": 290817, "content": "喝完大酒也不敢倒头就睡，卸了妆才敢趴床上……     熬夜必须敷面膜，用家里最贵的霜……     擦了眼霜才敢大笑，眼角细纹永远是斗智斗勇的敌人……\n毕竟是25岁的老女人了 ……", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1383560}, {"id": 291073, "content": "不能通宵了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1391764}, {"id": 291329, "content": "头发少了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 950981}, {"id": 291585, "content": "看的越来越淡了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1393247}, {"id": 290818, "content": "离少林寺越来越近了", "image": null, "praise_count": 25, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1340554}, {"id": 291074, "content": "再也不敢通宵了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1346364}, {"id": 294146, "content": "记忆力衰退...", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1410516}, {"id": 290819, "content": "越来越不想去主动尝试新的东西", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1188167}, {"id": 291075, "content": "单身久了会上瘾", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1334158}, {"id": 291587, "content": "心思变多，总是为情所困了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1192633}, {"id": 292355, "content": "一个人规律的生活，不想被打扰。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1397952}, {"id": 292611, "content": "修复了只吃不胖的bug！", "image": "img/option/option/20180714171305tjGBhbQ4UgqSz6Wl", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1325723}, {"id": 294147, "content": "难交朋友...", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1410516}, {"id": 291076, "content": "越来越跑不动了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1334158}, {"id": 290821, "content": "觉得自己真的老了", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 649267}, {"id": 291077, "content": "皮肤过敏症状严重了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 545614}, {"id": 290822, "content": "所谓心态越来越好，其实也就是没有目标可悲的得过且过。", "image": null, "praise_count": 33, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 970221}, {"id": 291078, "content": "视力开始模糊不清了，尤其是晚上~\n不知道什么叫痛了，只有折磨和压抑~", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1284195}, {"id": 290823, "content": "更加习惯孤独、自由生活", "image": null, "praise_count": 31, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 638791}, {"id": 291079, "content": "完全变了一个人", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1391780}, {"id": 290824, "content": "不买小年轻的衣服了。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1385854}, {"id": 291080, "content": "能意识到的都不叫变化", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1372281}, {"id": 291336, "content": "脱发了", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1367543}, {"id": 290825, "content": "肚子突然就大了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1385793}, {"id": 291593, "content": "晚上对爱爱都么兴趣了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1369563}, {"id": 291082, "content": "习惯一个人，更怕生病，怕生活不充实", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1391798}, {"id": 291083, "content": "宽容", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1300852}, {"id": 291595, "content": "自律变得困难", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 761850}, {"id": 291084, "content": "蹦不动迪。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1384637}, {"id": 291085, "content": "感覺自己越來越年輕了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 481913}, {"id": 290830, "content": "精力不够用了，原来通个宵睡一上午精神抖擞。现在每天睡七个小时都感觉精神不够", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1121867}, {"id": 291086, "content": "不想谈恋爱了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1250431}, {"id": 292110, "content": "错过的就错过了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1396613}, {"id": 290831, "content": "从关心最新的话题，掌握最新的流行语，到关掉大部分资讯来源，只读经典。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1386953}, {"id": 291087, "content": "越来越孤独!", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1391837}, {"id": 290832, "content": "以前想跟上司争对错，坚持自己的观点，还吵架；现在，我认真听着，做好自己的事", "image": null, "praise_count": 55, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 126152}, {"id": 291088, "content": "很多事情都看开了，不过挣钱的冲动越来越强！", "image": "img/option/option/20180706072215G90v4XwyOtVMUmil.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1386637}, {"id": 291600, "content": "真切感觉年轻真好", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1393350}, {"id": 292112, "content": "上学的时候通宵k歌，第二天睡一早晨就能恢复，现在熬夜晚一点，就感觉两三天都缓不过来", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1396683}, {"id": 290833, "content": "心理疾病跟新产生的正能量在博弈", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1391299}, {"id": 291089, "content": "胡子一天不刮不行", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1391854}, {"id": 290834, "content": "变肥了瘦不回去", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1352265}, {"id": 291090, "content": "作为男生竟然越来越瘦了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1374422}, {"id": 290835, "content": "慢慢地能处理好人际关系了，学会了拒绝，却丧失了了解这个世界的热情。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1391301}, {"id": 291091, "content": "醒的越来越早。周末不能避免。能睡回笼觉的概率下降", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 266480}, {"id": 290836, "content": "熬不动夜", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1322907}, {"id": 291092, "content": "妇科病开始来了……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1390820}, {"id": 293908, "content": "总觉得自己最小", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1338360}, {"id": 290837, "content": "脾气越来越差", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1391306}]}